    <h2>Help Section - Ocean View Resort Reservation System</h2>
    <p>Welcome to the Ocean View Resort Reservation System. This guide will help you understand how to use this system effectively.</p>
    
    <h3>How to Use:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Login:</strong> Enter your username and password to access the system.</li>
        <li><strong>Add New Reservation:</strong> Fill in guest details, select room type and dates to create a new reservation.</li>
        <li><strong>Display Reservation Details:</strong> Enter a reservation ID to view complete booking information.</li>
        <li><strong>Calculate Bill:</strong> Enter a reservation ID to compute the total stay cost based on number of nights and room rates.</li>
        <li><strong>Help Section:</strong> This page provides guidance on how to use the system.</li>
        <li><strong>Logout:</strong> Safely close the application when you're done.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>System Features:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>User Authentication (Login)</li>
        <li>Add New Reservation</li>
        <li>Display Reservation Details</li>
        <li>Calculate and Print Bill</li>
        <li>Help Section</li>
        <li>Exit System</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Contact Support:</h3>
    <p>If you encounter any issues or have questions about using the system, please contact support at support@oceanviewresort.com or call +94 11 123 4567.</p>
